<br>
*edited* ezboards jacked up a part, so had to correct it mmk*<br>
<br>
To start, I Haven't had internet connection on my comp for a few weeks, due to some comp troubles. So never checked my email til today and saw a friend pointin this thread out.<br>
<br>
I don't know who logged me on, nor do I care why. I already moved on with my life the day it happened, was sort of a god-send, telling me to get off of my ass before I end up 20 and still living with my parents.<br>
<br>
So, since I am bored I'll tell a story of that day. At the time I wasn't happy with being an officer, being an officer to loons means you get bunch of shit put on your shoulders, fun stuff right?..turns a diversion from life into another life full of more drama then the real one. Not my idea of fun, so I wanted out. Bad timing? Definitely. I felt like shit for leaving, betraying or leaving behind friends isnt a thing I like to do..but I felt it was necessary if I wanted to see PoP before I got tired and quit. Sort of like a repeat of my leaving ADD, which some peeps have mentioned in this thread I'm sure. I 'brought down ADD', makes sense right? I symbolically left due to a disagreement with a close friend who was GL, and some friends follow suit and this ends a guild...k, no. I got used as an excuse, but never said anything about it cause I was content with just playing the game for what it was, but some peeps like to revel in the thought of me causing the destruction of a flaming zeppelin.<br>
<br>
PL to lvl 65 eh? hmm, not like I sat there and slept while he did the dmg and healed, we both played our parts, I could have gone elsewhere and lvled if I had to. I'm not retarded and don't sit around lfg often, I take opportunities that are presented. Seph and I helped each other lvl because we both knew we could pull all nighters and have fun and talk to each other without any arguments, if that classifies as PL'n then I got PL'd by all of my friends sometime in my short career. I screwed my relations with some peeps in guild cause they thought we were trying to exclude ourselves and screw them, so I defend us and keep peeps off of Seph's back like a friend does and I don't let them bother him cuase I know he doesn't need to worry about shit. I'm sure somewhere in there I used him to lvl me so I can leave, also..quizas.<br>
<br>
The BoC? ahh, yes...the thing I dreamed of getting, spending all nighters helping the guild as the only tank online every night. Honestly, I didn't deserve it..I had just gotten Blasph blade the same night as AoW blade and I loved Blasph 10x more cause BoC isn't all that it is made up to be, low proc rate, etc. But I couldn't let someone who had just joined guild 3 days or so before win the first one (which would be his 2nd aow loot) and knowing that he had a view of loot that I didn't agree with...so I blew my points, me so evil..i know. I shall die in my sins.<br>
<br>
But what happened the night I got 'hacked' or 'destroyed my char'? The missing links? So i reluctantly posted up an open-ended post on the boards, basically a riddle of my mind saying that I didn't like my direction and wanted a new one, which I later found out was taken as a flame against RiP and people thought I was flaming them and puttin them down, which wasnt the original intent and was taken out of context. I have a bad habit of postin content that is hard to understand and is always taken the wrong way...strike 3 for me<br>
<br>
so In 4 hours (8pm to 12am roughly) I went from explainin to RIP why I left and the mass tells to the point of me getting my stuff 'taken' or me delving myself (hi, i cant zone 3 times wihtout crashing let alone kill myself 500% of exp..you do the math)...quotations cause some people won't like me saying hacking, but no matter. Seph tells me on a twink..I'm like ok, thats not cool, cause I don't trust peeps sayin they twinks. Saying this and that, guilt trippin me...i expected his respone, cause it is a normal response from any human being...I feel even more like shit about the ordeal..I get cussed at a little over some officer bulllshit thingy I told seph once that I wasn't worrying about when i left, and it oddly had no part in me leaving (the real reason was a loss of faith in something that has no relevance to this thread, only to bring up more flames, which is unnecesary and has no point to this thread.)<br>
<br>
So I let him go on, then he asks for me to give him the BoC...i'm like no (no as in I won't give to &gt;him(have fun with whats given to ya, and not material possession or fierce competition with others..which ruins a game, also this acted as a test to my true friends, someone wh ocared wouldnt' come at me upset and instead would ask me why, try to change my mind, or wish me well, and thats what I knew I would find in Blood, which would justify me passing the boc to him, but that wouldn't happen cause i'm greedy right?) or I could have given to sephrok who just got thru cursing at me while I was busy on a raid, without trying to find a different means for ends (if this was seph's intent I dont know, heated moments fucks all parties' creditibilty, so i don't blame him for being upset), or keeping it for myself. <br>
<br>
So the night goes on, get a few tells from twinks, why? mains work better cause at this point its hard to trust twinks that i've never heard of. So some names get on ignore....while on way to Emp with wraith I get telled by Zeik, inquiring about the BoC...everything so centered around this one item...couple hundred kpp item is more important then any ties with friends i guess...so I answer no...since I was still in that decision thingy I talked about a few lines up...and didn't feel I had to give him a solid answer, didn't think it would matter, I wanted to blow it off til the next day when peeps would think straight..cause anyone with half a brain would figure I was busy fending off tells to worry about a piece of loot that I view as trivial in my worldly pursuits.<br>
So, we get to emp...Ten makes sure I understand that I can't loot a rift...which I didn't care about...all things come in time and I am patient, and didnt care much for VT. Emp goes off without a hitch, saw a part of wraith that the flamers never get to see, a large mass of people working together always intrigued me, even more so then a few has (the 18 man ntov slaughter i was proudly part of)<br>
<br>
So, I'm like on offtank duty...anyone who knows the emp fight knows I'm over in a corner next to priests and tanks doing nothing but hittin low dps or no dps. Loot is done, they loot all the rifts, I don't move, i dont ninja, mass tele is done, but mine gets bugged (if a wizzy redid mass-tele while you had one up it bugs it, dont know if thats been fixed or not?) K no prob..i'm left with 1 druid and 1 war in room...we can group up and evac..didn't happen. I die, and then my computer crashes...this happened alot and most peeps in Rel would kid me about it, cause I would disappear during parts of raids while sittin at my comp rebooting and rebooting trying to get it to run, but thats minor and has no point (other then what Nerve used as flame bait for me, saying I'd show up at end of raids for loot, which would seem true, one time being that the power went out and I about lost it cause I would miss our 4th killing of AL, I finally get back online to find that they went ahead, cause Seph never waited on me cause he knew I wouldn't get back but he said i could bid..so likke a smart person i bid, even tho i had every right to..since i cleared in, i tanked the statics, i just miss a trivial 1 mob that drops the loot..i'm so in hte wrong there right? but that stuff is trivial,and happened months before this incident and that loot is gone so it doesn't matter)<br>
<br>
So to recap my ramblings, I left rip for certain reasons, I felt bad, I get farewelled,cussed, flames, and confused tells..I left not even thinking about the boc..I don't look at loot from a 'it was given to you perspective'...but I learned that much of my woes would be caused by my BoC...so I disregarded Seph and Zeik's inquiries about the BoC...shame on me...I go LD at midnight...I go to bed, to get rest for school cause I could just log on and get rez the next day...Wraith spots my char in ssra shortly after midnight (prolly thinkin i was doing CR)...they notice 'me' acting peculiar, they notice 'I' am being rude and saying odd things and they see 'me' give my BoC to Doobmon, zeik's twink, or someone, i wouldn't know who exactly since 'i' wasn't 'me' and I have no hard proof of that, and someone else does, who isn't me.<br>
<br>
So I log on at my usual time, 3:30 cst (stupid indiana and their not using Daylightsavings time)....I noticed I'm at 96% exp..wtf...k so i petition that somehow I lost exp...5mins later I notice I am lvl 60..even more wtf. So I'm like wtf and wtf and talkin to friends asking how I should go about petitionin, I get to ssra, a kind friend in wraith rezzes me after I pay for coffinin from a soloer...I notice no gear on my corpse except for a few pieces..Me: wtf.. so I sit and petition that something hapened. GM comes to me, not because of my petition, oh no..but because someone had already petitioned way before me saying I wasn't 'me'..k /boggle..so I take tally of all my stuff missing/stolen/deleted who knows what...and I count 16 weps, including my epics (which was my only item I was truly proud of owning), 5/6 of my wearable gear gone or deleted, (cof, rubi belt, amyg mask, boc)..so I'm like damn. Didn't go about blaming peeps, constant tells about me being lvl 60 and why, and me in my shocked stupor telling them I have no clue. of course everyone asks if someone had my account info...hell if i knew...so I stated to a few friends that only possible person could have been Seph..he at one time had my info for using me when i disappear at night (since I was one of the only tanks, i felt obliged to help out guild this way, by lettin him tank me if need occurs) but I got thinkin about it and I realize that its doubtful he knew or knows or whatever..so I didn't openly blame him, only did what would be expected of me and get pissed off at the thoguht of him doing it..hi basic human nature.../wave<br>
<br>
So I email VI's contact-a-pos-GM..and I get response 4 days later saying I could kiss their ass..so I log in, give my shit to my friends and tell them I'm thru...starting a new leaf with healthier diversions..(girls? quizas), I make the customary farewell pic of every highlight of my career, which shows some of the happiest times in my career, shit that makes you emotional to think back on. Then I get to thinkin about it, and I realize theres no point in arguing my point of view cause obviously it looks like I screwed everyone and did it as a last ditch effort to scam peeps..which is uncharacteristic of me, to those who know me on a real level instead of a fictional persona that eq develops of everyone. So I say why even bother...then I get these little emails, saying 'Hi this is soandso, download this virus scanner'..i'm like riiight, i don't download shit for no reason...then I ask that person in game about their email, gasp they had no clue..so someone was posing as my personal and best friend in game, who I held as a dear friend, tryin to persuade me to not blame Sephrok, makes sense..I don't really blame Seph either, still don't. So I call this pissant out and he goes all 'they'll never know, I don't know what you talkin about cause U don't know me' and so on. <br>
So I give up on the subject and decide not to mess with it any further. Which is hypocritical of me right now cause I'm posting this long ass post to pass time, which means I went against what I said I wouldnt' do (except for in a few emails to closest of kin online or with the fake emailer)<br>
So time goes on, I get email from seph with details of how I placed blame on him as last ditch effort to leave and sell my gear without consequence, about how I ninja'd a rift (hey gurunt, how many did you loot? oh thats right, all of them while i stayed in corner being good guy) and how he knew all about the fake Grimsoar emailing me even tho only Grim knew about it..So I laugh at the thought of it all and I reply tellin him to quit emailin me cause I'm puttin it all behind me. Makes sense right? I had no way of proving innocence cause this game doesn't provide a way, so why try.<br>
<br>
Am I bitter about this whole mess? No, only thing I hate is that htey posed as my best friend in a email to me, which is lame and stole pp from my bank that I was going to give t oa friend to help them out..but couldn't cause it was obviously gone. Do I find this ironic? definitely, ironic that I got screwed, got called out in emails from the mystery figure that i got screwed, got fake emails, got an essay from my ex-guildleader that I was screwing him..and all because of a BoC  ....that had I been givin 24 more hours would have been in Bloodshaww's hand and would still be in his hands.. and I would instead be miserable playin EQ, but hey in that pseudo world that never happened I would have my CoD, BoT and HoH flags, what rotten luck...wow hmm k maybe good luck<br>
<br>
But nah that couldn't happen, this is EQ...I screwed myself out of 14 months of hard work, sleepless night, endless worry, lower grades in school, fervorously helping others, takin my loot where I could to make myself the best which in turns makes me a bigger help to othres and ending all that by going out with a bang against someone who I was gonna meet in real life had I been old enough? Doesn't make sense to me. I had no vendetta, so quit saying I did. Just cause 'I'm 15 or 16 years old and smart' and just because someone who does drugs religiuosly and refused to go to ssra 80% of the time says so and has a checkered past that makes me out to be an angel, but personal attacks are cliche, but hey first response was a personal attack on me anyways so im' allowed to be a hypocrit right now <br>
<br>
Hail, back in your ass with the resurrection of a flame, mebe this post sheds some light on those who try to figure out my character...and instead they'll know how weird, confusin, and jacked up this whole situation is and why I never tried defending it. Caused its hella jacked. And I'm glad my reason to play EQ was taken away by a childish person /golfclap<br>
<br>
